OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FA snowboarder with motor neurone
OL,7,Fdisease (MND) is training in a last-
OL,8,Fditch effort to become the first
OL,9,Fperson with the condition to compete
OL,10,Fin the Winter Paralympics.
OL,12,FDavy Zyw, 38, is hoping to take part
OL,13,Fin the Milan-Cortina Games in 2026, as
OL,14,Fdespite his progressing condition, he
OL,15,Fcan still comfortably race down snowy
OL,16,Fterrains at breakneck speed.
OL,18,FMr Zyw, who lives in Edinburgh, was
OL,19,Fpreviously a competitive snowboarder,
OL,20,Fbut this was brought to an end by a
OL,21,Fknee injury.
