OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FHe was diagnosed with MND in 2018, and
OL,7,Fsays the condition encouraged him to
OL,8,Fgo back to his passion.
OL,10,FHe is now racing on the international
OL,11,Fpara snowboard circuit, and training
OL,12,Falongside Team GB athletes, in a bid
OL,13,Fto qualify for the games.
OL,15,FIf he succeeds, he will be the first
OL,16,FUK Paralympian with MND in any sport,
OL,17,Fand the first Aline snowsports athlete
OL,18,Fwith the disease, anywhere in the
OL,19,Fworld.
