OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FHe has finished on the podium in
OL,7,FFinland over the last few months, and
OL,8,Fhas climbed to fourth place in the
OL,9,FEuropa Cup rankings.
OL,11,FTo have a chance of qualifying, Mr Zyw
OL,12,Fmust finish on the podium at upcoming
OL,13,Fraces in Switzerland and Austria in
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FAfter that, he would qualify for next-
OL,17,Ftier events and possibly the World Cup
OL,18,Fraces in Canada.
OL,20,FHe said: "This time last year it was a
OL,21,Frogue dream.
