OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,F"Now I'm a contender. I'm improving
OL,7,Fall the time ` and that's something I
OL,8,Fnever expected to see after being told
OL,9,FI had MND."
OL,11,FMND has affected his hands, arms and
OL,12,Ftorso. He also faces severe fatigue,
OL,13,Fcramping, muscle wastage, and loss of
OL,14,Fdexterity.
OL,16,FHe said: "I can rip down a snowboard
OL,17,Fcross course at full speed, but I need
OL,18,Fhelp putting my gloves on, or zipping
OL,19,Fup my jacket.
