OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,F"That's the reality of my MND ` I am
OL,7,Ffocusing on what I can do, rather than
OL,8,Fon what I can't."
OL,10,FHe added: "On the mountain, there's no
OL,11,Fsympathy. None of the everyday baggage
OL,12,Fof MND. When the helmet goes on, we're
OL,13,Fall just athletes ` and that feeling
OL,14,Fgives me a new life."
OL,16,FHaving spent weeks abroad this season,
OL,17,Fhe gives credit to the support of his
OL,18,Fwife, Yvie, and their family.
