OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FHe said: "My wee boy keeps asking what
OL,7,Fmedals I'm bringing home. Being away
OL,8,Ffrom them is the hardest part by far.
OL,10,F"When you're living with MND, every
OL,11,Fday with your family is priceless.
OL,13,F"That sacrifice weighs heavily ` but
OL,14,Fthat's how much this dream means."
OL,16,FHe learned snowboarding at the Hillend
OL,17,FSnowsports Centre in Midlothian,
OL,18,Fcompeting in freestyle, and gained
OL,19,Fsponsorships, but his knee injury
OL,20,Fended his competitive hopes.
