OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FHe said: "MND brought me back to
OL,7,Fsnowboarding. It's given me freedom
OL,8,Fagain ` something that takes me far
OL,9,Faway from the dark places this disease
OL,10,Fcan take you."
OL,12,FHe added: "It keeps me up at night and
OL,13,Fgets me up in the morning. To become
OL,14,Fthe first person with MND on the
OL,15,FParalympic stage wouldn't just be my
OL,16,Fachievement ` it would be for the
OL,17,Fwhole MND community."
