OL,6,FHe is supported by his twin brother,
OL,7,FTommy, who travels with him while he
OL,8,Ftrains and competes, and he has had
OL,9,Ffinancial support from crowdfunding
OL,10,Fand his employer, Berry Bros & Rudd, a
OL,11,Fwine and spirits merchant, which has
OL,12,Fraised more than #700,000 for MND
OL,13,Fcauses.
OL,15,FHe has encouraged people to support
OL,16,FDoddie Aid, an annual January
OL,17,Fchallenge founded by former Scotland
OL,18,Frugby captain Rob Wainwright, who was
OL,19,Fa close friend and former teammate of
OL,20,Frugby legend George "Doddie" Weir, who
OL,21,Fdied of MND in 2022.
