OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FThe challenge involves participants
OL,7,Flogging their miles through running,
OL,8,Fcycling, or another activity, while
OL,9,Fraising funds for MND research.
OL,11,FMr Zyw said: "January can be a dark
OL,12,Fmonth.
OL,14,F"Doddie Aid gets you moving, connects
OL,15,Fyou with others, and raises millions
OL,16,Ffor the people who need it.
OL,18,F"Everyone should sign up ` pay #20,
OL,19,Fget a snood to keep your chin warm,
OL,20,Fand join a community doing something
OL,21,Fbrilliant."
