OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FHe added: "MND is not incurable ` it's
OL,7,Funderfunded. Every mile logged is a
OL,8,Fstep towards changing that.
OL,10,F"I'll be doing mine on the slopes, but
OL,11,FI'd encourage everybody to take part
OL,12,Fin their own way."
OL,14,FMr Zyw says qualifying will be tough,
OL,15,Fbut that he did not anticipate making
OL,16,Fit as far as he has already.
OL,18,F"I thought I wouldn't even be here
OL,19,Fwithin two years of diagnosis, and now
OL,20,FI'm racing for a Paralympic place," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
