OL,3,CSnowboarder hopes to become first with
OL,4,CMND to compete in Winter Paralympics
OL,6,F"This disease has taken so much, but
OL,7,Fit's also given me one last chance to
OL,8,Flive the dream I had as a kid.
OL,10,F"If I can get to the Paralympics, it
OL,11,Fwill put MND on the global stage. I
OL,12,Fowe it to everyone living with it. I
OL,13,Fowe it to my family.
OL,15,F"And I owe it to the kid who grew up
OL,16,Fat Hillend, Midlothian, thinking
OL,17,Fanything was possible."
